{
  "stem": "9245.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was very important to have weapons, as I said.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm repeating it that, first of all, with a weapon you could do-- you could obtain more weapons.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could also obtain more food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't forget it was getting towards winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were no food in the fields.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is how it happened that there are quite a few Jewish guys and girls that got organized.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They obtained weapons in exchange for clothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They went to their places of work and places of where they lived, and they got clothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for the clothing, you know, the farmers, all of them had weapons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The majority of weapons were hunting rifles and revolvers, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they obtained, they got organized, and there were about 11 of them, nine boys and two girls.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they went into a farmer's house, and they took away her sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That angered her a lot, and she decided she is going to do something about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she went to the [GERMAN] to the place of where the Germans were, you know, they were having their ruling place, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she went there and she complained.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She says that Jews are roaming the forest, and they are robbing and they are stealing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And why don't the Germans do something about it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They send out a couple Germans with a Ukrainian group, and they were chasing that particular group.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they caught up with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they-- one night, nine-- eight of them were sleeping in the barn, and the two girls with the boy were sleeping in the house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They caught them, and they did a horrible death to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They cut off their ears.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They cut out their tongues.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
